OL,4,Cleft with nothing - is your plan safe?
OL,6,FVictims of bankrupt funeral companies
OL,7,Fwere left with nothing, ITV News
OL,8,FConsumer Editor Chris Choi reports
OL,10,FPeople who bought funeral plans from
OL,11,Fcompanies that collapsed have told ITV
OL,12,FNews they are calling for a public
OL,13,Finquiry.
OL,15,FSafe Hands Plans Limited and One Life
OL,16,FFuneral Planning left tens of
OL,17,Fthousands of customers without
OL,18,Ffunerals - and without the money
OL,19,Fthey've paid.
