OL,4,Cleft with nothing - is your plan safe?
OL,6,FAfter struggling to pay for her
OL,7,Fhusband's final arrangements,
OL,8,FChristine Hughes, 77, paid for her own
OL,9,Ffuneral.
OL,11,FShe did it for peace of mind, but what
OL,12,Fshe has got is worry. The company Safe
OL,13,FHands Plans Ltd went bust two years
OL,14,Fago.
OL,16,F"It cost me #4095, and it was
OL,17,Fbasically all the money that I've got
OL,18,Fin the bank. When I paid for my
OL,19,Ffuneral plan, I had about #100 left,"
OL,20,FChristine told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
