OL,6,F"I wanted a proper send off so my
OL,7,Ffamily could say goodbye properly. Now
OL,8,Fthat's not going to happen because I
OL,9,Fcan't get that money again to pay for
OL,10,Fanother funeral."
OL,12,FChristine said she felt others like
OL,13,Fher hadn't been supported in the wake
OL,14,Fof Safe Hands Plans Ltd's collapse.
OL,16,FShe said: "I feel hurt, I do feel let
OL,17,Fdown and I think I speak for many
OL,18,Fpeople when I say we feel that we've
OL,19,Fjust been pushed to one side and
OL,20,Fnobody's interested."
