OL,3,CVictims of bankrupt funeral companies
OL,4,Cleft with nothing - is your plan safe?
OL,6,FITV News has learned that the
OL,7,Fadministrators of the collapsed Safe
OL,8,FHands Plans Ltd are about to make an
OL,9,Fannouncement on available funds - but
OL,10,Fit's expected to be only a fraction of
OL,11,Fwhat plan holders paid.
OL,13,FAn ongoing fraud investigation into
OL,14,Fthe collapsed firm is underway, with
OL,15,Fmillions of pounds believed to be in
OL,16,Fthe Cayman Islands.
OL,18,FSince July 2022, funeral plans have
OL,19,Fbeen regulated by the Financial
OL,20,FConduct Authority, including
OL,21,Fcompensation if firms go bust.
