OL,6,FSafe Hands Plans Ltd, with 70,000
OL,7,Fcustomers, collapsed in 2022. One Life
OL,8,FFuneral Planning Ltd, with 13,700 plan
OL,9,Fholders, went bust after officials
OL,10,Frefused to authorise the company under
OL,11,Fthe new rules two years ago.
