OL,3,CVictims of bankrupt funeral companies
OL,4,Cleft with nothing - is your plan safe?
OL,6,FFinancial campaigner James Daley from
OL,7,FFairer Finance says officials should
OL,8,Fhave known money was at risk and
OL,9,Fshould have acted.
OL,11,FHe said: "Many people are still
OL,12,Funaware they have got plans that are
OL,13,Fworth nothing.
OL,15,F"It is time that the government steps
OL,16,Fup and says, 'We let a lot of people
OL,17,Fdown here, let's look at why that
OL,18,Fhappened, make sure it never happens
OL,19,Fagain in any other sector, and try to
OL,20,Fhelp those people who have already
OL,21,Fpaid for a funeral'."
