OL,3,CVictims of bankrupt funeral companies
OL,4,Cleft with nothing - is your plan safe?
OL,6,FThe latest estimates reckon one in six
OL,7,Ffunerals are now paid for via a
OL,8,Ffuneral plan.
OL,10,FAny bought after July 2022 from
OL,11,Fauthorised providers will be protected
OL,12,Fby the Financial Services Compensation
OL,13,FScheme - this means your money is
OL,14,Fprotected if the company fails.
OL,16,FYou can check whether your funeral
OL,17,Fplan is covered by Financial Conduct
OL,18,FAuthority (FCA) compensation rules
OL,19,Fhere.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
