OL,6,FThe FCA website also has warnings
OL,7,Fabout funeral plan firms that did not
OL,8,Fbecome authorised, and therefore
OL,9,Fshould not be selling plans.
OL,11,FWe asked finance campaigner James
OL,12,FDaley of Fairer Finance to give some
OL,13,Ftips for those buying funerals in
OL,14,Fadvance.
OL,16,FFairer Finance's James Daley gives a
OL,17,Fbreakdown of what to consider when
OL,18,Fbuying a funeral plan
OL,20,FCheck that the firm is FCA regulated
