OL,6,FTo make sure of this, look on the
OL,7,FFCA's register. If the company is on
OL,8,Fthere, then you can buy with
OL,9,Fconfidence and know your money will be
OL,10,Fprotected if the firm goes bust.
OL,12,FBe sure of what is covered on the
OL,13,Ffuneral plan
OL,15,FThere is a lot of difference in the
OL,16,Fmarket. Some guarantee all the core
OL,17,Fcosts, such as the cost of a
OL,18,Fcrematorium.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
