OL,6,FOthers, such as a contribution plan,
OL,7,Fjust have a pot of money to put
OL,8,Ftowards those third-party costs.
OL,10,FStay aware of flexibility
OL,12,FPeople's circumstances do change, and
OL,13,Fsome funeral plans will not move with
OL,14,Fyou.
OL,16,FSome firms do not allow you to move
OL,17,Fyour plan, and you may face a hefty
OL,18,Fcancellation fee.
