OL,6,FA HM Treasury spokesperson said: "Once
OL,7,Fconcerns were raised about the funeral
OL,8,Fplan market, we made it illegal to
OL,9,Fsell pre-paid funeral plans without
OL,10,Fauthorisation from the Financial
OL,11,FConduct Authority ` protecting 1.6
OL,12,Fmillion customers and their families.
OL,14,F"As the Serious Fraud Office is
OL,15,Fconducting a criminal investigation
OL,16,Finto Safe Hands Plans Limited, it
OL,17,Fwould not be appropriate for the
OL,18,Fgovernment to comment further at this
OL,19,Ftime."
